List subscribable options associated to the given server ID.

USAGE:
  scw dedibox option list [arg=value ...]

ARGS:
  server-id         Server ID of the subscribable server options
  [zone=fr-par-1]   Zone to target. If none is passed will use default zone from the config (fr-par-1 | fr-par-2 | nl-ams-1 | all)

FLAGS:
  -h, --help   help for list

GLOBAL FLAGS:
  -B, --beta             Enable beta mode
  -c, --config string    The path to the config file
  -D, --debug            Enable debug mode
  -o, --output string    Output format: json or human, see 'scw help output' for more info (default "human")
  -p, --profile string   The config profile to use
